==================
SmileTAG Changelog
==================

December 26, 2005 -- Version 2.3
=================================
- Admin Panel added
- Message Moderation
- Valid XHTML 1.0 Transitional

December 7, 2005 -- Version 2.2
=================================
- Patch for multi-language support, now utf-8 is fully supported (previously only iso-8859-1)

November 21, 2005 -- Version 2.1
=================================
- Bugfix for PHP5 user only, smilies was disappearing


November 14, 2005 -- Version 2.0
=================================
- Engine rewritten
- Template system
- A big enhancements for major features
- and lot more, see www.smiletag.com/features.php for complete list


September 14,2002 -- Version 1.1
================================
- Message manager bugs fixed


September 12, 2002 -- Version 1.0
=================================
- Outputs valid XHTML 1.0 Transitional code
- Admin control panel for :
	* Easy message deletion
	* Easy nick/ip address banning
	* Easy board configuration


September 02, 2002 -- Version 0.9
================================
Initial release